 />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtLGgT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtLGgT</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個POST<br />\n好撚辛苦同班人講左成兩粒鐘<br />\n我唔要求佢地支持, 我唔想佢地散播失敗主義<br />\n阻住其他巴打既行動POST"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"好多三毛，又話咩啲支持嘅都係著黑衫<br />\n<br />\n有落場都知至少七成巴絲係上班族衫/出街衫喬裝，三毛功課都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7c12eef4634f738783f3c3212cb4a9d6a3bce4","tid":1392411,"uid":130695,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:49:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n跟本本地果500隻三毛就係咁互推<br />\n政府跟本好撚驚公政員+各界一齊罷工"},{"pid":"c62ed99a9d17cc299a117050c83b2c942b8e45d6","tid":1392411,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"根本如果唔搞不合作運動<br />\n罷工只會雷聲大雨點小"},{"pid":"8f2c64712d98b1e6312af899174a7ed488f7fbfe","tid":1392411,"uid":32983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n應該要塞<br />\n俾多個理由打工仔正當罷工"},{"pid":"c8926df85b30d53ef2e0e1a12c421217462ab513","tid":1392411,"uid":274475,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a7c12eef4634f738783f3c3212cb4a9d6a3bce4","tid":1392411,"uid":130695,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:49:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n跟本本地果500隻三毛就係咁互推<br />\n政府跟本好撚驚公政員+各界一齊罷工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"上面果隻忍氣吞聲，仲有黑騎士，主線任務呀傻西，幾隻來來去去係咁帶風向，起底全部都係叫人唔好乜唔好物嘅三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92981ae93919c8f1dd355a71578c1649292413d","tid":1392411,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9e44fe6706298d2ab6ec67259888d56eb8e8cf8","tid":1392411,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee46caed96921eb275a62f3e5fa16c673484e25","tid":1392411,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"3f4d0fc0f83cffd70664e01dfae9c6937c69eb28","tid":1392411,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc83cc46e23beeb1242e018bd14ff14edf3835f","tid":1392411,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"ec3ed6ab3155c57f4c5c4ad7417ab6f5e156e299","tid":1392411,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afefe9a03ceb78f011b789537c8056599f0aaee5","tid":1392411,"uid":267044,"like":9,"dislike":17,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"dbd89969119e9ef2ead4e42adb47edd587535486","tid":1392411,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"明明730塞鐵市民反應好好，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有落場嘅巴絲都會見證到</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>今日突然大量三毛狂推反塞鐵，有何居心?</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n對比起前兩次塞鐵，今日已經多左市民理解<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384246</a><br />\n<br />\n【現場觀察】今次真係好多人 支持塞港鐵不合作運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385071</a><br />\n<br />\n有人係地鐵塞緊既車箱播鏗鏘集⋯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384491</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家！今次塞地鐵好有用，我足足遲左2個鐘先返到工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abuPuEU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abuPuEU</a>"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a